The personalised models were solved using the finite element method. Specifically, a quadratic-linear interpolation scheme was employed for the displacement and hydrostatic pressure variables, respectively. The base and epicardial multipliers were approximated with quadratic triangular elements while the endocardial multiplier was a scalar. All problems were solved using \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
